{"tid":1610061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[千祈唔好咁做] 東鐵拆鐵進化指南","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T00:32:23.000Z","uid":147748,"like":139,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"553f2b84afd386c26844e9394b793a2da6c046e6","tid":1610061,"uid":147748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"話說其實拆鐵除咗拆站之外<br />\n如果大家有工具有能力有熱誠<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記得唔好</span>進入路軌範圍同黨鐵玩遊戲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ULxe0s6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULxe0s6.jpg&h=309bd3da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東鐵沿線路軌兩邊有唔少嘅消防閘口<br />\n會有綠色牌寫住一個數字加一個英文字母<br />\n例如19.2D就係下行線嗰邊(東面)距離紅磡19.2公里嘅嗰道門<br />\n下次搭東鐵可以留意下路軌兩邊啲紅色閘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鎖住道門嘅有一個鎖 通常一個半米長嘅大力剪就夠剪斷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxZtktm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxZtktm.jpg&h=f0f5a8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果冇剪鉗但有其他工具 <span style=\"color: red;\">記得唔好手多多</span>試吓拆吓個門鉸<br />\n拆左之後入去<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好為所欲為呀</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得千祈唔好搞破壞以身試法</span> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要做奉公守法既好市民</span></span><br />\n唔好好似班着綠色衫嘅暴徒成日入侵鐵路系統打良好市民破壞建築物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd420f81836614296e63597d1382bcdf6f0dd01","tid":1610061,"uid":147748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"自推十連!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7effcdf94a1b461b82814f95cda4f8340e32bc5","tid":1610061,"uid":67303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:13:38.000Z","msg":"[破窗效應]真槍呢單野一定要有咁大煲咁大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1608423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1608423</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21c1e9b8a518ec90d40faef574fd728e051ce22f","tid":1610061,"uid":147748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96df8c4255e92a0427ffa9a792fa71d091f1d56","tid":1610061,"uid":147748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02bf8a29c43110b63aed3f501c13649a7177c68","tid":1610061,"uid":147748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg